706117f-a.text:
Synagogue, Ocean Parkway at Sheepshead Bay Rd., B'klyn.
Sept. 23, 1941.
P.L. Sperr, photographer

This photograph is in the wrong place. It seems to be at Bay Parkway several miles from where it should be at Sheepshead Bay Road. However, Sheepshead Bay Road no longer physically exists next to the Synagogue, therefore, the coordinates should place it between Oceanview and Neptune Avenues.
